<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1178] get_slice calls do not close files when finished resulting in &quot;too many open files&quot; exceptions and rendering C unusable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1178</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;insert ~100K rows.  Read them back in a loop.  Notice &quot;too many open files&quot; exceptions in log.  SSTableSliceIterator is never closing the files.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12466596">CASSANDRA-1178</key>
            <summary>get_slice calls do not close files when finished resulting in &quot;too many open files&quot; exceptions and rendering C unusable</summary>
